org.el.ghostnetfishing.view

Class PersonBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.el.ghostnetfishing.view.PersonBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Named
 @ConversationScoped
public class PersonBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Backing bean for Person entities.

    This class provides CRUD functionality for all Person entities. It focuses purely on Java EE 6 standards (e.g. @ConversationScoped for state management, PersistenceContext for persistence, CriteriaBuilder for searches) rather than introducing a CRUD framework or custom base class.
